         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Correspondence among alumna relating to a memorial, protesting

		  compulsory residence in Sage College; replies of college presidents relating to

		  women's residence requirements at their colleges; account of the preparation of

		  the memorial and evaluation of its effect by Ellen Coit Brown.</p>
      </scopecontent>
